verbose_text: Although the overall lung phenotype of RP-Fgfr1 mice appeared very different from that of RPM mice, mainly because of the reduced SCLC and the presence of LADC (XREF_FIG D and 3E), we detected enhanced expression of ALDH1A1 in BLs and ALs (XREF_FIG E-3G); BLs and ALs of RP-Fgfr1 mice also showed high levels of EGFR, this in striking difference with LADC (XREF_FIG I-3K).
